Sssd
=======

This module configures SSSD, and authentication service that provides LDAP and KERBEROS facilities.
It has been developed under Ubuntu 10.04.

It is able to setup:
- sssd service
- multiple authentication "domains"

Conventions
-----------
This modules is making user of standard Debian/Ubuntu tools for updating the pam stack, knowingly auth-client-config.
It enforces SSL connection for querying LDAP, hence the dependency below.

Dependencies
------------

* Concat git://github.com/ripienaar/puppet-concat.git
* SSL module

